Title : [Macroglossia in plasmacytoma. A case report].
Date : 1986
Publication_type : Journal Article
Abstract : A case of macroglossia is presented the underlying cause of which was a generalized amyloidosis due to a plasmacytoma. Differential diagnosis of macroglossia comprises acromegaly, myxoedema, tumours, allergic reactions, inflammatory diseases, congenital muscular hypertrophy, glycogen storage defects and amyloidosis.
